  with a semi circle on top;
  diameter of the semicircle exactly matches the
  width of the rectangle.  Find the dimensions
  <m>w \times h</m> of the Norman window whose
  perimeter is <m>$a\text{in.}</m> that has
  maximal area.
</p>
